        <div class="faq-container">
            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-question">
                    <h3>What services do you offer?</h3>
                    <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>We offer a comprehensive range of beauty and wellness services including haircuts, coloring, styling, makeup, facials, and more. Visit our services page for a complete list.</p>
